<h1>Downloadable data</h1>

<p>These data files are generated daily from the subset of our data that we consider to be completed.</p>

<p>The data is available on several formats, but only the PROIEL XML export format faithfully represents all the information available.</p>

<ul>
  <li><%= link_to "Schema file", "/exports/text.xsd" %> <span class="warning">(Please note that this schema is not yet considered stable and may be modified at any time.)</li>
  <li><%= link_to "Definition of the morphological annotation", "/exports/morphology.xml" %></li>
  <li><%= link_to "Definition of the dependency structure relations", "/exports/relations.xml" %></li>
  <% Source.find(:all).each do |s| %>
    <li>Data for <%= s.title %>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "PROIEL XML", "/exports/#{s.code}.xml" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "TigerXML", "/exports/#{s.code}-tiger.xml" %> <span class="warning">(Experimental!)</span></li>
        <li><%= link_to "MaltXML", "/exports/#{s.code}-malt.xml" %> <span class="warning">(Experimental!)</span></li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
